      <pre contenteditable="true">console = #console.
find `the needle `in `the haystack ->
  get the n-th position by applying haystack.indexOf on needle;

needle = 1
haystack = {1 2 3}
result = find the needle in the haystack
console.log result

if test `passes `do this `and `else `do that ->
  that ?= []
  passes = check test
  passes ? do this : do that;
;

value `of n ->
  if [n.] do [
    print with console.log the text 'true'
  ], else do [
    print with console.log the text 'false'
  ]
;

value of 5</pre>
